OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showery
OL,6,Frain spreading east this evening,
OL,7,Fmainly across the west with some high
OL,8,Fground snow. Becoming dry with clear
OL,9,Fperiods during the early hours. Cold
OL,10,Fwith some frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMainly dry with some sunshine
OL,13,Fin the morning. Dry but cloudier in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Strengthening winds
OL,15,Fextending northeast in the evening.
OL,16,FRather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
